# arcMinute

- _arcMinute(n)_

Answer _n_ times one _arc minute_, the constant representing one sixtieth of a `degree`.

```
>>> 1.arcMinute
1/10800.pi

>>> 1.arcMinute
1/60.degree

>>> 3/2.arcMinute
90.arcSecond
```

* * *

See also: arcSecond, degree, pi

